        <h2>Detection of Fake Physical Certificates using a Blockchain-Based Certificate Verification and Issuer Validation System</h2>
        <p class="authors"><strong> Ankit K C</strong> , Deepesh Bhandari, Rojalina Priyadarshini, Pramod Kumar Meher</p>
        <p class="venue">Presented at<em>2024 IEEE International Conference on Blockchain and Distributed Systems Security (ICBDS)</em>, 2024</p>
